data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
This wizard will guide you through the process of creating a new Server Group.
Server Groups allow you to organize your SQL Servers for easy use within the SQL admin toolset. Many of the tools allow you to specify a server group as the target of their operation. For example, you could create a server group for all your accounting SQL Servers and then select that group in tools like Backup Status to report on all the SQL Servers in the group.
